='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91metoo%ef%bc%9a%e8%ae%a9%e6%88%91%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e4%bd%a0%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%b0%e9%9f%b3-%e4%bb%8e%e5%8c%bb%e9%99%a2%e3%80%81/0731a5/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A5-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A5-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A5-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91metoo%ef%bc%9a%e8%ae%a9%e6%88%91%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e4%bd%a0%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%b0%e9%9f%b3-%e4%bb%8e%e5%8c%bb%e9%99%a2%e3%80%81/0731a6/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A6-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A6-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A6-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A6-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91metoo%ef%bc%9a%e8%ae%a9%e6%88%91%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e4%bd%a0%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%b0%e9%9f%b3-%e4%bb%8e%e5%8c%bb%e9%99%a2%e3%80%81/0731a7/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A7-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A7-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A7-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/0731A7-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>同日，在另外一则博文中，微博@清华常江写道：</p>\n<blockquote><p>#I’ll be your voice# 这个姑娘是一起强奸案的受害者。她讲述了自己跟抑郁、耻感、荡妇羞辱和歧视性的制度抗争的经历，以及米兔带给她的力量。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/清华常江0731B-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-591313\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/清华常江0731B-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/清华常江0731B-1.jpg 827w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/清华常江0731B-1-300x253.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/清华常江0731B-1-768x647.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>以下为贴图文字版部分内容摘录。请点击图片查看原文——</p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">常江老师，这是我的遭遇，metoo 运动在中国开始后，我陷入了一种失真感。我看见了微博上的浪潮，也看见了身边的人对它的熟视无睹。我把自己的故事实名写出来，只是为了让更多人看到，让更多人反思这件事。我能做的不多，我只能成为为她们中的一员。</span></p></blockquote>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-17 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-17 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-17 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-17 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-17' class='gallery galleryid-591292 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a h